      "introduced_terms": [
        "half_life"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "对于均值回归策略，还需要知道一个关键数字：",
        "<term id=\"half_life\">半衰期</term>。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "half_life"
      ],
      "id": "s041",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "半衰期 = ln(2) / κ",
        "κ是均值回归的速度。κ越大，回归越快。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
